         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141"><!-- p4l4-r8 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De risu apto atque inepto</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>
      ¶ De risu apto atque inepto. Rubrica. 8
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>SAlomon in prouerbiis. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>11. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e125">Quasi per
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>risum stultus operatur scelus.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e131"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e133"> Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>tonas in ecclesia. c. i. Qui addit scientiam
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>addit laborem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e142"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e144"> 3. c. Tempus flendi: et tem
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>pus ridendi. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e150"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e152"> 7. c. Sic sonitus spinarum ar
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>dentium sub olla sic risus stulti. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e162">¶ Isocrates in exhortationibus. c. 2 in prin
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>Risum precipitem non diliges: illud emm amens est </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e172">¶ Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiast. c. 21 Fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>tuus in risu exaltat vocem suam: vir autem
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>prudens vix tacite ridebit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e180"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e182"> 27. c. Risus pec
        <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>cantium in delictis peccati. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e192">¶ Catullus. c. 5. Risu inepto res ineptior nla est </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-d1e197">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d84141-Qd1e201">¶ Auctor vel deus for. hone. vite. c. 8. Reprehen
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>sibilis risus. est si immodicus et si pueriliter ef
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>fusus. Odibilem facit hominem risus: aut
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>superbus: aut elacus: aut malignus: aut fur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>tiuus: aut alienis malis euocatus. Risus si
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>ne chachino sit. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
